00:16:28,739 --> 00:16:32,350
Hidup itu singkat dan ibu bisa berubah pikiran.

246
00:16:33,180 --> 00:16:34,249
Bisakah?

247
00:16:35,580 --> 00:16:36,779
Kalau begitu,

