350
00:21:42,149 --> 00:21:43,219
Apa?

351
00:21:43,219 --> 00:21:45,530
- Keadaan menjadi terlalu panas.
- Aku setuju.

352
00:21:45,530 --> 00:21:47,429
Mari kita tenang sedikit.

353
00:21:47,459 --> 00:21:49,159
Para ibu benar,

354
00:21:49,159 --> 00:21:51,699
- begitu juga para menantu.
- Benar.

355
00:21:51,699 --> 00:21:53,899
Bagaimana jika kita mendinginkan suasana

356
