360
00:22:02,480 --> 00:22:05,209
jadi, ada lebih banyak wanita di sini daripada pria.

361
00:22:05,209 --> 00:22:07,310
Aku melihat panel kita

362
00:22:07,310 --> 00:22:09,419
- dan melihat seorang pria.
- Benar.

363
00:22:09,419 --> 00:22:12,689
Aku ingin dengar pendapat pria.

364
00:22:12,889 --> 00:22:14,889
Pak, apa kabar?

365
00:22:15,020 --> 00:22:16,990
Bisa ambil mikrofonnya?

366
00:22:17,520 --> 00:22:18,560
Pak?

367
00:22:18,560 --> 00:22:19,830
- Aku?
