- Tunggu.

388
00:23:04,770 --> 00:23:07,840
Pukul berapa dramanya dimulai?

389
00:23:07,939 --> 00:23:10,780
Aku mengamati istri dan menantuku.

390
00:23:10,780 --> 00:23:12,109
- Apa...
- Ada apa?

391
00:23:12,109 --> 00:23:13,879
Seratus persen

